metadata.name: Verification
metadata.description: This badge signifies verified authenticity and credibility. It's awarded to individuals or entities that have undergone a rigorous verification process, ensuring their legitimacy in the digital space. Possessing this badge enhances trust and confidence among users interacting with the verified account or profile.

metadata.name: Entry Ticket
metadata.description: The badge acts as a limited-access pass to exclusive events, content, or communities. Holders of this badge gain entry to restricted areas, unlocking opportunities to engage with premium experiences or interact with curated content within a digital ecosystem.

metadata.name: Premium Membership
metadata.description: A symbol of privilege, this badge grants access to elevated features, services, or perks within a platform. Holders enjoy enhanced benefits beyond standard users, fostering a sense of belonging and recognition within a premium community.

metadata.name: Diploma
metadata.description: Awarded for completing educational courses or programs, the diploma badge represents a milestone in learning. It showcases an individual's dedication and achievement, often linked to skill development and knowledge acquisition in specific domains.

metadata.name: Attendance
metadata.description: This badge acknowledges active participation in events or gatherings. Recipients gain proof of their presence and engagement, making it a digital memento for networking, community involvement, and memorable experiences.

metadata.name: Contributor
metadata.description: The contributor recognizes active participation and contributions to collaborative projects or communities. It celebrates individuals who have made meaningful impacts and fosters a sense of belonging within a group effort.

metadata.name: Authorship
metadata.description: Awarded to creators and authors, the authorship establishes ownership and originality of digital content. It safeguards intellectual property rights and offers a traceable record of creative works.

metadata.name: Scam Alert
metadata.description: The scam alert badge serves as a warning against fraudulent or malicious activities. It highlights potential risks and signals caution to users, helping to prevent interactions with untrustworthy individuals or platforms. Be wary of users who own the scammer badge.

metadata.name: Certification
metadata.description: The certification badge signifies successful completion of professional assessments or tests. It demonstrates expertise and competence in a particular field, contributing to personal and career growth.

metadata.name: Trophy
metadata.description: A symbol of accomplishment, the trophy badge is earned by achieving noteworthy feats or goals. Holders can proudly display their achievements, showcasing mastery, success, or recognition in various endeavors.
